BMON(1)                     General Commands Manual                    BMON(1)

NNAAMMEE
       btmon - Bluetooth monitor

SSYYNNOOPPSSIISS
       bbttmmoonn

DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       bbttmmoonn is Bluetooth monitor

UUSSAAGGEE
       btmon [options]

       Options:
         --rr, ----rreeaadd <file>      Read traces in btsnoop format
         --ww, ----wwrriittee <file>     Save traces in btsnoop format
         --ss, ----sseerrvveerr <socket>  Start monitor server socket
         --ii, ----iinnddeexx <num>      Show only specified controller
         --tt, ----ttiimmee             Show time instead of time offset
         --TT, ----ddaattee             Show time and date information
         --SS, ----ssccoo              Dump SCO traffic
         --hh, ----hheellpp             Show help options

AAUUTTHHOORR
